<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-1411] FBUtilities.hexToBytes() doesn&apos;t accommodate odd-length strings.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1411</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a problem when a user specifies ByteOrderedPartitioner with an odd-length initial token (like &quot;0&quot;).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12472038">CASSANDRA-1411</key>
            <summary>FBUtilities.hexToBytes() doesn&apos;t accommodate odd-length strings.</summary>
